'''Ditwar Logas''' was a [[sentientologist]] of some repute during the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] era.

[[Obo Rin]] once claimed to have studied under Logas at the [[Three Rings University of Social Sciences]]. However, [[Imperial Intelligence/Legends|Imperial Intelligence]] [[Major/Legends|Major]] [[Herrit]] claimed in a communiqué to [[Lord/Legends|Lord]] [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] that Three Rings was not a genuine university, but a business that sold worthless diplomas via computer order.

